data.description: FANTASTIC LOCATION ON THE BEACH SIDE JUST STEPS TO THE BEACH WITH DIRECT ACCESS! THIS LOCATION IS AWESOME! MINT CONDITION HOME WITH NEW SIDING IN 2019, AND COMPOSITE DECKING. 2ND FLOOR W/ BRIGHT OPEN FLOOR PLAN TO INCLUDE GREAT ROOM WITH FIREPLACE, GREAT ROOM WITH NEWER SLIDING DOORS, SPACIOUS KITCHEN W/ NEWER STAINLESS STEEL APPLIANCES, DOUBLE OVEN W/ CONVECTION AND CENTER ISLAND, GRANITE COUNTERTOPS + BAMBOO WOOD FLOORING. ALL BEDROOMS HAVE AN ATTACHED FULL BATH. TONS OF UPGRADES TO INCLUDE HUNTER DOUGLAS BLINDS, HOT TUB, ADDITIONAL CONCRETE WITH SAND PIT, LOW MAINTENANCE FENCING. GENERATOR HOOKUP, CUSTOM TILE WORK IN THE ENTRY AND LEDGES, MARBLE TILE BACKSPLASH IN THE KITCHEN. HUGE PRIMARY SUITE W/ 3 CLOSETS + PRIVATE BALCONY & SPIRAL STAIRCASE TO ROOF TOP DECK WITH AMAZING VIEW OF THE CHESAPEAKE BAY BEACH. LOFT AREA IN ADDITION TO BEDROOM COUNT - GREAT AREA FOR OFFICE/ PLAY AREA.  HUGE 455 SQ FT 2 CAR GARAGE + EXTRA STORAGE AREA. TANKLESS GAS HOT WATER HEATER. 2 ZONE GAS HEATING.
